  "texts": [
    "Impact of fine-tuning epochs.",
    "Figure 6 shows that, the model's performance on the test datasets improves with more fine-tuning epochs, and start to plateaus after 10 epochs.",
    "Given the prolonged training time, we set the fine-tuning epochs to be 20 by default.",
    "Impact of data diversity.",
    "To investigate the influence of fine-tuning data size on model performance, we vary the number of samples and epochs so that, in each setting, the model is trained on roughly the same number of tokens."
